{"TopicId":105991,"ForumId":16,"TopicTitle":"Can asteroid overheat and explode?","CreatedByName":"Joseki","CreatedById":123945,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-29T14:31:22Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"Joseki","CreatedById":123945,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-29T14:31:22Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI was pulling an asteroid with 4 Nerv and it immediately explode due to overheating, is it normal? \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_huh.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:confused:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://images.akamai.steamusercontent.com/ugc/37496212290893500/8353B5C1053E5729693AC62CB5DD34F5A6828C32/\u0022 alt=\u00228353B5C1053E5729693AC62CB5DD34F5A6828C32\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"KatzOhki","CreatedById":73492,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-29T14:59:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003ELOL! That\u0027s hilarious! I guess that\u0027s what happens when meteors burn up in our atmosphere, but you really cooked it!\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Feradose","CreatedById":111211,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-29T17:44:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EPotatoroids have a heat tolerance of 2500, which is way higher than the melting point of ore, right, devs?\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Joseki","CreatedById":123945,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-29T18:32:16Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EIt exploded half a second after I pushed the Z button. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Captain Sierra","CreatedById":74666,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-04-29T20:50:49Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Joseki\u0022 data-cite=\u0022Joseki\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003EIt exploded half a second after I pushed the Z button. \u003Cimg src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_undecided.gif\u0022 alt=\u0022:huh:\u0022\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/blockquote\u003E\u003Cp\u003ENervas, by dint of being a nuclear freaking reactor blasting its coolant into space as propulsion, generate a fair amount of heat. My best guess is that some weirdness happened in how the heat transferred around your craft and ended up using the rock as a heatsink.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}